<br>
GENERAL SETTINGS<br>
<br>
We've set the board to be in English, with the time specification (the &quot;clock&quot; for timing and dating all posts and administrative actions) of GMT-8, or Pacific Standard Time. To change either parameter, simply click on the pull-down menu next to the item and select your preference.<br>
<br>
FORUM FIND SETTINGS<br>
<br>
We have set your board to be searchable -- meaning that it will appear in our Search feature. You will need to enter a description and keywords in the spaces provided. <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.ezboard.com/forumfind/help_aboutsearch.html">Click here</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> for more information on Forum Find.<br>
<br>
If you would like to be &quot;private&quot; (not searchable), uncheck the box next to &quot;Make My Community Searchable!&quot;<br>
<br>
SECURITY SETTINGS<br>
<br>
We set &quot;Registration Required&quot; as the default for membership -- meaning that anybody can come to the community, but only those users who post become members of your board. Under the other security options, we've enabled Show Number of Members, Show Poster IP (provides administrators with the IP address associated with each post), Post Flood Safety Check (helps discourage spamming) and the Profanity Filter (note that you can add words to the filter).<br>
<br>
A final note -- notice at the bottom of the page is the link to the Log File, which you can review. It will log all the major administrative actions you take on the board (adding or deleting forums and topics, moving content, etc.). <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.ezboard.com/help/community/security_faq.html">Security FAQs</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
